overview: Many people can be seen walking around the yard adjacent to a railway station. A train with several passenger cars pulls up to the station. The camera pans, photographing quite a few people and horse-drawn two- and four-wheeled vehicles. The picture ends as a four-wheeled horse-drawn vehicle approaches the camera position. A coachman sits on the box in the front, and in the seat behind him is president Teddy Roosevelt waving at the crowd.
title: President Roosevelt's Homecoming
